Preliminary to make life easy:
sudo apt-get install sfml-dev

to:
	compile to obj files                              link the files							put exec	    clear the obj files
g++ -c -std=c++17 -I ./include/ ./src/*.cpp && g++ *.o -lsfml-graphics -lsfml-window -lsfml-audio -lsfml-system -pthread -o ./binFile/linuxBuild && rm *.o

to run the file:
./binFile/linuxBuild
